overview: On April 1st GCW presents For The Culture 3 live on FITE! The event features pro wrestling stars such as HitMakerz, Shane Taylor Promotions, Bryan Keith, Bill Dixon and more.  The first announced matches of the lineup are:  Tasha Steelz vs Big Swole  AJ Gray vs Darius Lockhart  JTG vs Rich Swann  2 Cold Scorpio vs Bryan Keith  Hoodfoot vs Billy Dixon  Trish Adora vs MJ Jenkins  Hitmakerz vs Shane Taylor Promotions
title: GCW For The Culture 3
